{"blocks":[{"key":"fvuj6","text":"Vortex, followed by incubating for 20 minutes at 50°C.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2s4ot","text":"Mix briefly by vortex and centrifuge for 8 seconds in mini centrifuge. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
